# Governance

This project starts as a generated engineering repository. It is prepared for future Knowledge Source onboarding but is not automatically onboarded.

## Governance Principles

- Certified Knowledge remains the source for generated engineering rationale.
- Project-specific decisions must be documented locally.
- Future reusable observations should be prepared for Knowledge Source onboarding.
- Publications, templates, and generated documents are not canonical knowledge.

